<br>
Gabrielle smiled at Empress Xena.<br>
<br>
&quot;Hey, don't worry about her, she's just upset. You are not as bad as you think as things. Give yourself a break.&quot;<br>
<br>
The Lykastian's tone was warm and almost motherly. She contiued eating until finished, she picked up her plates and put them in the washing tub.(the sink). Gabby took the bread from the oven, and let it cool while Empress Xena finished up her meal.<br>
<br>
After that, Gabrielle sliced the bread and placed some honey spread into a bowl for dipping the bread in. She sat down and passed Xena a few pieces from the plate before taking a piece for herself and dipping it into the honey spread. <p>§Gabrielle§<BR>
